official_title: To designate the week of September 16, 1990, through September 22, 1990, as "National Rehabilitation Week".

summary.text: Designates September 16 through 22, 1990, as National Rehabilitation Week. Urges each State Governor and local government chief executive to issue proclamations calling upon their citizens to observe such week with appropriate ceremonies and activities.
